      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are not carrying a weight for no reason; you are the only thing that exists, and the weight is the only thing that keeps you from falling into the void. The house is not empty; it is full of the silence you are screaming into, and the only way to fill it is to stop trying to fill it with anything else. The lights are not on because there is no one to see them; they are on because you are the only one who can see them, and seeing them is the only way to prove you are still here. Existence is not a burden; it is the only thing that matters, and you are the only thing that can carry it.",
